title: Top Places to visit in Ponnur, Andhra Pradesh
content: Ponnur is a town in the Guntur district of the Indian state of Andhra Pradesh. Kilari Venkata Rosaiah – YSRCP Party is the present MLA of the constituency, who won the 2019 Andhra Pradesh Legislative Assembly election from the YSRCP Party.
